item.title: I'm Stuffed
item.description: Disclaimer: These are my own opinions of these restaurants, this post is not sponsored! This weekend was a very filling one. Each day I was eating something yummy, somewhere! Friday My brother and my cousin went to Blue Fin Sushi. They have an all you can eat lunch pretty cheaply for $17.84 CAD. No limits or anything! I was supposed to go with them last week but I ended up missing it.
